title: Gold-trimmed leather armour

properties.name: description
properties.value: Gold-trimmed leather armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Leather armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from easy Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.

content:
A player wearing gold-trimmed leather armour.

Gold-trimmed leather armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Leather armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from easy Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.
